Kaggle credentials are missing or Kaggle CLI is unavailable.
Manual fix:
1. Create a Kaggle account.
2. Go to Account settings.
3. Create API token.
4. Put kaggle.json in ~/.kaggle/kaggle.json on Linux/WSL or C:/Users/<USER>/.kaggle/kaggle.json on Windows.
5. Run the command again.

